This is not a phishing site. It is a test/development project with no malic=
ious content, no credential collection, and no intent to imitate any servic=
e.
The detection appears to be a false positive.

2. My Cloudflare account has been suspended

After the false phishing detection, my Cloudflare account (email: oliverxia=
ozhen@outlook.com
) was automatically restricted:

I cannot add new domains

I cannot purchase domains

Some dashboard functions are disabled

Pages project is blocked

I confirm that my projects do not violate Cloudflare AUP, and this suspensi=
on is likely caused by the false phishing flag.

3. Request

I respectfully request:

A manual review of my Pages project

Restoration of my Cloudflare account access

Confirmation that the phishing flag has been removed

My account is used for normal development purposes, and I believe this is a=
n automated false positive.

Thank you very much for your time and assistance.

Best regards,
oliverxiaozhen@outlook.com

